Name: Rabisco
About the game: Help Ms. Rabisco to find the moon's lost stars and bring back the light, in this cute but dangerous world, inspired by the World's Hardest Game. Massive world with 100 levels and 300+ screens of precise running and secrets. Super tight control schemes designed for both keyboards and controllers. Cute crayon art style with bright colors and hand drawn lines. Hardcore difficulty 20+ types of enemies and interactable objects. Lovely soundtrack inspired by Bossa Nova, the famous Brazilian musical genre. The night was so bright it could be mistaken by the day.
